org.nd4j.linalg.api.blas

Interface Level1

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseLevel1, CpuLevel1, JcublasLevel1

    public interface Level1
    Level 1 blas implementations. Incx and other parameters are inferred from the given ndarrays. To avoid boxing, doubles are used in place of normal numbers. The underlying implementation will call the proper data type. This is a fortran 95 style api that gives us the efficiency and flexibility of the fortran 77 api Credit to: https://www.ualberta.ca/AICT/RESEARCH/LinuxClusters/doc/mkl81/mklqref/blaslev1.htm for the descriptions
